umber Nine Ticket','Get all other trophies in the game'),(8,199,37.38,3,'The Right Way','Play the whole game with tank controls. Tim demanded this trophy'),(8,200,92.38,1,'\"What I did back in the fat days is none of your business. You know the rules.\"','Talk to Eva about how she got stuck here'),(8,201,82,1,'\"Gets the aggressions out, doesn\'t it?\"','Use the hole punch'),(8,202,62.64,1,'\"Scaring the living is technically against the rules, but we all do it.\"','Scare the living a few times'),(8,203,60.13,1,'\"It\'s like I\'m not happy unless I\'m breathing in the thick, black, nauseating fumes...\"','Talk to Glottis about cravings'),(8,204,85.13,1,'\"Lousy bony fingers!\"','Get the balloon twister to pop a balloon'),(8,205,67.91,1,'\"I squeezed down one of these tubes, like a pixie!\"','Talk to Brennis about how he got to the machine'),(8,206,30.5,1,'\"Well, I could do something bad right now if that would help.\"','Try to dig up some dirt on Meche'),(8,207,63.6,1,'\"Precisamente, amigo.\"','Learn of a nefarious plot'),(8,208,52.12,1,'\"Join or Die! Again!\"','Receive a message from Eva'),(8,209,44,2,'\"\'ARROGANT FRAUD\' doesn\'t work\"','Try to guess Domino\'s password a few times'),(8,210,48,1,'\"Run you pigeons! It\'s Robert Frost!\"','Try to intimidate the pigeons'),(8,211,43.09,1,'\"The marrow of these trees, Manny, they suck it out, it\'s like cement!\"','Ask Glottis about the tree farm'),(8,212,45.81,1,'\"We only have one mop.\"','Check your job qualifications with Celso'),(8,213,49.81,1,'...Used to scream like a banshee when the trade winds blew...','Ask Velasco about his eye patch'),(8,214,49.81,1,'\"Plus, we look good in these clothes!\"','Talk to Glottis about leaving'),(8,215,50.06,1,'\"Well, maybe just a sip...\"','Sample the Marillo de Oro'),(8,216,51.36,1,'\"We are all citizens of the same nation, and our king rides a pale horse.\"','Try to get a passport from Chowchilla Charlie'),(8,217,52.12,1,'\"YOU\'RE NOT EVEN LISTENING TO ME!!!\"','Ask Lupe about her organizational system'),(8,218,43.09,1,'\"It shone, pale as bone...\"','Look at the moon'),(8,219,45.81,2,'\"Consider it an homage.\"','Have Olivia recite one of your poems'),(8,220,49.81,1,'\"We\'re straight stingers, you know?\"','Talk to the worker bees about playing the game'),(8,221,42.08,1,'\"Here, let me hold that metal detector for you while you cry...\"','Listen to Carla\'s whole story'),(8,222,48.58,1,'\"Manny, we\'ve given up. All of us.\"','Talk to Membrillo about why he\'s still here'),(8,223,44.95,1,'\"Come to see how the big boys play, eh Manny?\"','Visit with Maximino'),(8,224,44.95,1,'\"So, sorry, but I don\'t do... \'odd jobs.\'\"','Try to convince Verago to help you out'),(8,225,44.95,1,'\"Oh Rusty Anchor\"','Have Glottis sing you the rusty anchor song'),(8,226,44.95,1,'\"ME, ME, ME-ME-ME!\"','Chant with the bees'),(8,227,44.95,1,'\"I wasn\'t always this color!\"','Talk to Chepito about how long he\'s been down here'),(8,228,44.95,1,'sniff sniff','Make the angelitos cry'),(8,229,43.7,1,'\"Save your breath...\"','Try to explain to Meche'),(8,230,44.95,2,'\"Okay, how much of this haven haven\'t you figured out, Calavera?\"','Get Domino to explain the racket to you'),(8,231,44.95,1,'\"IT\'S A BUST-ALL!\"','Talk to Chepito about his bartering tactics'),(8,232,44.95,1,'\"Stop showing off for the girl!\"','Try to beat Domino in a fair fight'),(8,233,44.95,1,'\"Happy trails, Captain.\"','See Chepito on his way'),(8,234,44.95,1,'\"I could walk out of this world and not look back...\"','Hold to your commitments'),(8,235,44.95,1,'\"I\'m getting out of here. This world\'s for suckers.\"','See Bruno on his way'),(8,236,44.95,1,'...so large','Meet the mechanics'),(8,237,41.7,2,'\"Oh, Lola...\"','Revisit the place where you left Lola'),(8,238,44.95,1,'\"THAT\'S NOT FUNNY!\"','Crack a joke'),(8,239,44.95,1,'\"Manuel! Is everything okay?\"','Play with the radio'),(8,240,44.95,1,'\"Here we go again!\"','Other random talk'),(8,241,44.95,1,'\"Another lin